social_posts.post_text: @newgeneralcafe has abundant flowers donated from yesterday’s wedding at The Alfond Inn. Come and take however many you like and make your own bouquet today!
When it rains it’s actually a great time to explore Winter Park in Florida.

Want to buy one of these bikes?  Walk and roll up to 18mph while cruising the streets!  A brisk walk can move you at 18mph on the flats!  Come try at the Winter Park Bike Tour!  Like and follow for more cool videos!
When the Plum Islanders come to town and ask if there really are peacocks here…

Everyone keeps asking if any of the bikes are for sale. We have some still in the box and a few used ones fully assembled ready to roll away for a discount!  If you’re interested reach out and we can discuss which color you would like to own! New ones from The Netherlands are $3000 euros.  Local discount here and free local delivery (and training too)!
Winter Park Bike Tour. Be sure to find out where we ride next time. Like and follow for more! #fyp #foryoupage #tour #memorialday
Stationary or on the road. Either way to get fit on the walking bike.
There are a few fully assembled ready to roll electric treadmill bikes available for $1000 for 66% off new price!
New collaboration with Mediterranos in the works. Best Pita in all of Florida. Follow and share to find out more! @_mediterranos #pita #bakery #orlandoflorida #summer
Had a great time with @_mediterranos inviting us to the @ucf.knights @novaathletics game at @fbcmortgage bounce house tonight in Orlando.
